{
  "stem": "27409.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My father's father, paternal grandfather, before the war, he had estate, with mill, forest.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he had, when the Romanian came in, they decorated him, with a high insignia, because his neighbor was Jancu Flondor, who became the minister for Bukowina, was an estate owner.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They grew up, my father, with his daughter, grew up together.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Afterwards, she married the minister of finance in Romania, Cancicov.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I remember, always to new year, they used to send a bottle of wine from their estate.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not in school, really, and not on the street.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You see, in the street, where we lived, were Romanian academics Our-- next-door was a high court judge, Stefaneli.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] Stefaneli was his son.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was a friend of mine.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Also, he was older.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We shared the same hobby.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Opposite from us was Baron von Anauch, whose wife was from the British Royalty.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we did not have, really, to deal with the ordinary Romanian.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The policeman was respectful, because my grandfather brought him up.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was an orphan.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He grew up.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And Diverse was our police officer, you see?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So it was this-- everybody knew us and respected the family.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "What year did you leave your primary school, your elementary school?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, in 1930.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had to pass entrance examination.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I-- during this summer, I passed with top marks.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Coming from the private school, you see, I had a better preparation than the others, which came from state school.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was-- I was supposed to go to the Realschule Number 2.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But in-- during the vacation, the school was closed for budgetary reasons.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So the top few, which were mostly Jews, were sent to the Realschule Number 1, which was a grant-aided school by the Romanian Orthodox Church.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
